interview_invitation.body:
Dear {{CANDIDATE_NAME}},

We are pleased to inform you that your application for the {{POSITION}} position has been shortlisted, and we would like to invite you for an interview.

Interview Details:
• Date: {{INTERVIEW_DATE}}
• Time: {{INTERVIEW_TIME}}
• Duration: Approximately {{DURATION}}
• Format: {{INTERVIEW_FORMAT}}
• Location/Link: {{INTERVIEW_LOCATION}}

What to Prepare:
• Brief introduction about yourself
• Examples of relevant projects or experiences
• Questions about the role and our company

Please confirm your availability by replying to this email within 48 hours. If the proposed time doesn't work for you, please suggest 2-3 alternative times.

We look forward to meeting you!

Best regards,
{{INTERVIEWER_NAME}}
{{COMPANY_NAME}} Recruitment Team
